From e84768db862057fe9949511ab3f55579a13221be Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Alok Singh <aloksing@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Fri, 27 Jun 2025 07:30:18 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] UPSTREAM: DP: wifi: ath12k: Refactor monitor hal specific
 structures

Currently, monitor hal tlv structures for both
monitor and data-path are intermixed.

This patch is intend to keep wifi7 specific tlv structers to
wifi7/hal_mon.h
and keep common structures in hal_mon_cmn.h
that apply across multiple chipsets,
ensuring reusability for future expansions like WiFi8.

Patch-dependency:
	0402-0005-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Refactor-monitor-pdev-ring-a.patch

Signed-off-by: Alok Singh <aloksing@qti.qualcomm.com>
